create /usr/share/applications/application.desktop to add it to desktop menu.
for example, the zotero.desktop entry is like

[Desktop Entry]
Name=Zotero
GenericName=Zotero
Comment=Reference Management(Standalone)
Icon=/home/kagami/Programs/Zotero_linux-x86_64/chrome/icons/default/default48.png
Exec=/home/kagami/Programs/Zotero_linux-x86_64/zotero
Type=Application
Terminal=false
Categories=Development;Internet;
Keywords=Document;Reference;
